    "The main advantage of SciANN is the possibility of defining the derivatives of the variables in physical equations 34, 35.",
    "Jagtap et al.",
    "36 introduced Conservative Physical Information Neural Networks (cPINNs) for nonlinear conservation laws.",
    "Kharazmi et al.",
    "37 introduced the Petrov-Galerkin formulation in PINNs and proposed variational physics-informed neural networks (VPNNs)."
